Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.15,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自分の殻を脱いでOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.67,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}追い求めた光へOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.74,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そうだ今日も　まだ知らない世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:33.70,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step One step One step
