Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:35.58,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那天和今天的道路太过不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:46.00,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}视线变得模糊 喉咙仿佛被堵住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:50.04,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}深吸一口气又缓缓呼出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:55.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step总是一切的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.65,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step通往无限的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:03.70,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}迈向遥远的从未见过的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:09.70,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step One step One step
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:20.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}停下脚步 终结就会轻易到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:26.10,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}但我不愿辜负你的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.85,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}甩开模糊的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.97,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}向前奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:52.55,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}好奇心和你一起牵着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:21:00.51,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}温柔的声音和眼眸又蕴酿出新的「一步」
