Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:13.27,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}迈向遥远的从未见过的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.92,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}让我们一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卸下自己的硬壳踏出One step
